Third Department,

May, 1981

(May 5, 1981) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Andrew Jenkins, Appellant, v Lawrence C. Kolb, as Commissioner of the New York State Department of Mental Hygiene, et al., Respondents.

— Application for writ of habeas corpus denied. Mahoney, P.J., Sweeney, Kane, Casey and Weiss, JJ., concur.
